        "description": {
          "value": "<div  class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>The howler emits a keening howl in a 60-foot cone. Each creature in that area must succeed on a DC <span class=\"rd__dc\">13</span> Wisdom saving throw or take 16 ([[/r 3d10]]) psychic damage and be @condition[frightened] until the end of the howler's next turn. While a creature is @condition[frightened] in this way, its speed is halved, and it is @condition[incapacitated]. A target that successfully saves is immune to the Mind-Breaking Howl of all howlers for the next 24 hours.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div></div>",
